## Release pipeline

GitHub Actions workflow at `.github/workflows/release.yml` triggers on tag push. It:
1. Builds for each platform.
2. Packages with the launcher / installer per platform.
3. Uploads to {DISTRIBUTION_TARGET}.

Manual release checklist before tagging:
- [ ] Version bumped in {VERSION_FILE}
- [ ] CHANGELOG updated
- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] Last-build smoke-tested on at least 2 platforms locally
- [ ] Asset license audit clean (no copyrighted music etc.)

